Tags:
  - Invocation=The Dispeller of Sin
  - Invocation=The Universal Elixir
By: Swami Sivananda
---
Man cannot live by bread alone; but he can live repeating the Name of the Lord
alone. ... One who does not do Smarana of Hari is a Neecha (low-born). The
day spent without the remembrance of His Name is a mere waste.
